WEBVTT

01:37.367 --> 01:40.662
Deference to the executive
cannot possibly justify

01:40.745 --> 01:45.625
the injuries to Mr. Mahmoud
or the death of his family members.

01:45.709 --> 01:50.421
If you do not say that this is wrong,
that this is unconstitutional,

01:50.505 --> 01:55.301
there is nothing to prevent this sort
of senseless tragedy from happening again.

01:55.385 --> 01:58.804
We ask for nothing more
than reform and oversight.

01:58.888 --> 02:01.057
Your ruling is a crucial first step.

02:01.140 --> 02:03.226
- Thank you.
- Thank you, Mr. Katyal.

02:03.309 --> 02:04.728
Ms. Dunbar.

02:10.483 --> 02:13.403
Mr. Chief Justice,
and may it please the court,

02:13.486 --> 02:17.281
the security of American citizens
is the reason our drone program

02:17.365 --> 02:19.534
and other covert operations exist.

02:19.617 --> 02:22.912
But that security
often comes with a cost.

02:22.995 --> 02:26.499
At this very moment,
the president is at Arlington Cemetery,

02:26.583 --> 02:28.918
laying to rest three Navy SEALs

02:29.001 --> 02:32.797
who perished on a mountainside
in Afghanistan.

02:32.880 --> 02:35.383
They gave their lives to save others.

